        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: The supplemental table S1 contains 1264 proteins identified in the PSD preparation (Synaptic junctional protein preparation). FIBA was found as Q99K47.\nPart of the fibrin matrix; currently a potential association with synapses is only based on several proteomic studies.. Experimental description: Briefly adult mouse brains (2-16 months, 20 animals, 10 g wet weight) were homogenized ... p. 915" ;
